This box has been a work in progress, he is where i'm at with it.  I  may 
leave it alone, i think it's as good as it will get.
 
Trying new things doesn't always make a box better, some of my best work  
was a year ago.  I just can't keep doing the same thing over and over, so i  
try new stuff.  Sometimes i hit the nail on the head and sometimes it's a  
step back.
 
-Steve
